:

1. *Pojavi* se u kancelariji tokom ručka. (He appeared in the office during lunch.)
2. Ona se *pojavila* u sobi bez ikakvog upozorenja. (She appeared in the room without any warning.)
3. *Pojavio* se novi problem sa kompjuterom. (A new problem with the computer appeared.)
4. Ne čekajući nikoga, *pojavila* se sestra. (Without waiting for anyone, her sister appeared.)
5. *Pojavljuju* se novi ljudi na sastancima. (New people are appearing at meetings.)